post_text: Good morning families, we are continuing to monitor the coronavirus situation and make adjustments in the best interest of student and staff safety. To help prevent the spread of coronavirus (COVID-19), we are cancelling all scheduled field trips and prohibiting spectator participation at extra-curricular events. If you have specific questions about an event, feel free to call the school or email the front office. Thank you for your understanding. We will continue to post updates as they come.

We are excited to announce we are planning to move to our new location in the Fall of 2019! Our new address will be 4747 Heatherdowns Blvd, Toledo, OH 43614.

To reserve your child’s seat for the 2019-20 school year, please complete your re-enrollment packet as soon as possible! Please note that the State of Ohio is now requiring every family to submit an updated Proof of Residency (POR) each year. To indicate whether your child(ren) will be returning or not for the 19-20 school year, please login to SchoolMint by visiting: http://accelschools.schoolmint.net or stop by the front desk!

post_text:
Shout out to David Bush with Madd Poets Society Inc. for volunteering time out of his busy schedule to speak to our middle school students. Messages of the day ~ Why can't you be an owner of a business? Why do you have to serve someone else in making their dreams come true and not your own? Do you want to work and make YOUR dreams come true or do you want to serve others the rest of your life in making THEIR dreams come true? Your education will determine, where you live, what you eat and what you drive!
#wordsarepower
text:
Shout out to David Bush with Madd Poets Society Inc. for volunteering time out of his busy schedule to speak to our middle school students. Messages of the day ~ Why can't you be an owner of a business? Why do you have to serve someone else in making their dreams come true and not your own? Do you want to work and make YOUR dreams come true or do you want to serve others the rest of your life in making THEIR dreams come true? Your education will determine, where you live, what you eat and what you drive!
#wordsarepower
